Adopted packages protected against dealing with breaking
changes across repos
Edits are tracked as part of Outcast repo
Backporting changes or importing bug fixes is out
of

If the Adopted package is from an Outcast Repo

At most only
one

be present.

g.title: Sheet.421
g.desc: Integrate packages allow for ‘mixing’ in the copied package s...
g.text: Integrate packages allow for ‘mixing’ in the copied package source code with the primary package’s source tree. For example the primary package has a src/bsp/MyBoard/ directory, and adopting an integrate package could copy to src/bsp/ArduinoOne/
